You know, I don't understand the complaint about pet's taking xp. I can solo Oranges very easy,especialy with the new pet healing. A fighter can normally only solo yellows. The xp works out about the same I think. What's bugging me is pet classes complaining about xp loss to pets, and tanks complaining that they can never solo oranges. Now someone may be able to provide hard stats that refute this, but in my experience it works out about the same.<P>--------------------<P>Elbarad<BR>Percival<BR>Dux Bellorum
